               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18670225-name-339" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18670225-name-339" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18670225-name-339" type="surname" value="EMERY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18670225-name-339" type="given" value="ENOCH"></interp>ENOCH EMERY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City Policeman</hi> 653). About half-past one in the after<lb></lb>noon of 7th February I saw the prisoner in St. Paul's Church Yard—he was very busy among the people—he went up to a lady, put his hand in her pocket, and took out this purse (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—I saw it in his hand—he put it into the side pocket of his coat—I took hold of him and called after</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186702250083"></xptr>
               <p>the lady—there was a hole in his pocket, and the purse fell to the ground—the lady said it was hers—I took him to the station and charged him with stealing the purse—he made no answer—a gentleman picked the purse up.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
